lassName\\\":\\\"text-xl font-bold text-olive-800 mb-6 flex items-center gap-2\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"💬\\\"}],\\\" 常見問題\\\"]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"space-y-3\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"details\\\",\\\"0\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"group border border-olive-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"summary\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"flex items-center justify-between px-5 py-4 cursor-pointer bg-olive-50 hover:bg-olive-100 transition-colors list-none\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-semibold text-olive-800 text-sm leading-relaxed pr-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"橄欖油開封後可以放多久？\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-olive-500 shrink-0 text-lg group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"▾\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"px-5 py-4 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed bg-white\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"高品質 EVOO 開封後建議在 60-90 天內用完，以保留最大多酚活性。研究顯示，開封後在室溫下儲存 3 個月，多酚含量下降約 40%。若您不常使用橄欖油，建議購買 250ml 的小瓶裝，而非 1 公升大瓶，避免多酚在您用完之前就已大量流失。\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"details\\\",\\\"1\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"group border border-olive-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"summary\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"flex items-center justify-between px-5 py-4 cursor-pointer bg-olive-50 hover:bg-olive-100 transition-colors list-none\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-semibold text-olive-800 text-sm leading-relaxed pr-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"橄欖油可以放冰箱嗎？\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-olive-500 shrink-0 text-lg group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"▾\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"px-5 py-4 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed bg-white\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"可以，而且是夏季最佳選擇。橄欖油在低溫（8-12°C）下可能出現白色結晶或霧狀，這是正常的物理現象（固態脂肪酸析出），完全不影響品質和風味。回到室溫後會自動恢復透明。注意：冰箱門的反覆開關造成的溫度波動，比穩定低溫更有害——建議放在冰箱深處，而非冰箱門的置物架上。\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"details\\\",\\\"2\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"group border border-olive-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"summary\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"flex items-center justify-between px-5 py-4 cursor-pointer bg-olive-50 hover:bg-olive-100 transition-colors list-none\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-semibold text-olive-800 text-sm leading-relaxed pr-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"橄欖油變混濁還能用嗎？\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-olive-500 shrink-0 text-lg group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"▾\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"px-5 py-4 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed bg-white\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"要區分兩種情況：(1) 低溫混濁（白色結晶/霧狀）——完全正常，回溫即恢復，品質無影響；(2) 室溫下的持續混濁、沉澱或懸浮物——可能是未過濾油中的天然微粒（正常）或氧化產物（問題）。判斷方法：做氣味測試，如果有油耗味、醋味或蠟燭味，代表已酸敗，請勿食用。高品質未過濾（Unfiltered）EVOO 本身就會有輕微混濁，這反而是多酚含量更高的指標。\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"details\\\",\\\"3\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"group border border-olive-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"summary\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"flex items-center justify-between px-5 py-4 cursor-pointer bg-olive-50 hover:bg-olive-100 transition-colors list-none\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"font-semibold text-olive-800 text-sm leading-relaxed pr-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"如何判斷橄欖油已經壞掉？\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-olive-500 shrink-0 text-lg group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"▾\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"px-5 py-4 text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed bg-white\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"橄欖油酸敗的三個感官指標：(1) 氣味——從清新果香/青草香變為「油膩感」、「金屬味」、「蠟燭味」或「醋酸味」；(2) 口感——喉嚨失去辛辣嗆感（Oleocanthal 消失），舌根苦感消退；(3) 顏色——從金黃/綠黃轉為深棕黃色（排除低溫結晶情況）。一旦出現氣味異常，無論視覺如何，都不應作為健康補充使用，可降級為高溫烹飪用途（但健康效益已大幅降低）。\\\"}]]}]]}]]}]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"24:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-olive-100\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h3\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-lg font-bold text-olive-800 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"📚\\\"}],\\\" 參考文獻\\\"]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"ol\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"space-y-2\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"li\\\",\\\"0\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-sm text-gray-500 flex gap-2\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-olive-400 font-medium shrink-0\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"[\\\",1,\\\"]\\\"]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Stabilization of phenolic compounds in extra virgin olive oil (Food Chemistry 2023)\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"li\\\",\\\"1\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-sm text-gray-500 flex gap-2\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-olive-400 font-medium shrink-0\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"[\\\",2,\\\"]\\\"]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Effect of packaging and storage conditions on EVOO quality (European Food Research 2024)\\\"}]]}]]}]]}]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"25:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"mt-10 pt-8 border-t border-gray-100 flex gap-4\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L2\\\",null,{\\\"href\\\":\\\"/blog\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-olive-600 hover:text-olive-800 font-medium hover:underline\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"← 返回文章列表\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L2\\\",null,{\\\"href\\\":\\\"/#subscribe\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"ml-auto inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-olive-700 hover:bg-olive-800 text-white text-sm font-medium px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl transition-colors\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"訂閱知橄週報 🫒\\\"}]]}]\